headline: 3 Big Reasons to Love Netflix (NFLX)
summary: Since June 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 97.4%. But one standout stock has nearly doubled the market - over the past five years, Netflix has surged 175% to $1,261 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 35.3% in the last six months thanks to its solid quarterly results, beating the S&P by 35.5%.
